      "\u003cp\u003eWe're an agile, fast-growing data engineering and analytics company headquartered in downtown Seattle. We build scalable solutions and models for companies that impact tens of millions of customers.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe’re looking for a talented full stack developer to join our small, collaborative team. You will have the opportunity to work on both front-end and back-end components across a variety of architectures, from single-page apps in React to API servers in Go. The successful candidate is detail-oriented, has excellent communication skills, loves to work on cutting edge technology and has a knack for problem solving.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYour Qualifications:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e4+ years of software development: Ruby / Rails, JavaScript frameworks, Go\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e2+ years of experience working with cloud based platforms and services such as AWS, Azure or Google Cloud Platform\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExperience with popular modern CI/CD tools\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExperience with building data pipelines and using big data frameworks is a plus\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMust be curious, tenacious and humble\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYour Responsibilities:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWork closely and with team members to build product and platform features\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eParticipate in project planning and customer discussions\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n",
