    title: 'Full Stack Developer',
    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePRINCIPAL RESPONSIBILITIES AND DUTIES:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFull Stack Developer\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDo you want to work with a group of badass designers, technologists and writers to create innovate websites and web applications?  We are seeking a strong Full Stack Developer who has a passion for building websites, single page applications, and working with API’s to make extremely fluid and functional software. You will be responsible for  building the front-end and back-end design of websites and software applications, and creating design plans for the user-facing side of applications, which controls look, feel, and function.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis role will be an integral part of the Development team and you will collaborate with  designers, marketers, and the entire company to solve problems and achieve meaningful results. As our team’s first full time Full Stack Developer, you will be expected to pick things up quickly, work efficiently, and contribute to the direction and future of our Development team. You’ll work on multiple client accounts in varying industries. You will have the opportunity to make a big impact both for your clients and on the company. Red Caffeine takes pride in making sure every team member’s voice is heard  and that everyone has the ability to shape their and the company’s growth path.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWho You Are\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePeople with a strong desire to learn a multitude of technologies and programming languages with a can-do attitude will thrive in this role. You  are a problem-solver who can work in a fast-paced, collaborative office environments alongside other engineers and developers.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePosition Responsibilities Include:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePlan and develop websites and web applications\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCreate software solutions\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eArchitect and implement solutions to complex client systems\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMaintain quality and ensure responsiveness of applications\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCollaborate with the rest of the team to design and launch new features\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMaintain code integrity and organization\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWork with databases; both maintaining, creating, and configuring them\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCode in various programming languages especially .NET and JavaScript\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTake low fidelity mockups and turn them into fully functioning end products and components\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDevelop immersive experiences for both mobile and desktop applications\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRequirements \u0026amp; Bonus Points:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDegree in Information Sciences, Computer Science, MIS, or related field of study (Experience/Portfolio can suffice)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e3+ years of application development and maintenance experience in a professional work environment\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHighly skilled, detail oriented Developer well versed in Object Oriented Programming \u0026amp; best practices\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExpertise with HTML5/SCSS/Javascript\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExperience in a back-end language such as Java, C++, etc. - C# preferred\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExperience with SQL queries and relational modeling/databases (RESTful API, MS SQL, etc.)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExperience with .NET \u0026amp; Visual Studio - a compatible CMS is a plus\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExperience with Umbraco or Razor is a huge plus\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExperience building real-world web application software and SPA’s\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExperience with at least one front-end application framework such as Angular, React, or Vue\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExpertise in reasoning about and cleaning data\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMeticulous attention to detail\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eGreat communication and organizational skills\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUnderstanding of security and data protection\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWorking knowledge of code versioning tools (Git, DevOps, SVN)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUnderstands how to manage/estimate time and deliver projects on schedule\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExperience with testing tools is a plus, but not required such as Jest, Jasmine, etc.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAny experience with Data Visualization tools or analytics dash-boarding is a bonus\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePerks:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMedical, dental, and vision benefits\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e401k matching\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eComplete freedom to explore and implement new technology ideas and solutions\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWork with a small group of dedicated Tech/Digital focused individuals who share your passion for technology\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCraft coffee and beer\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePing pong matches at will\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFlex-Time\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWork from home opportunities\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTransparent company financials\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOffice dogs\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eComplimentary beverages and snacks\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWork with a group of Badasses\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eRed Caffeine is an Equal Opportunity Employer\nMust be able to pass pre-employment, post offer background checks\nPrincipals only. Recruiters, please do not contact.\u003c/p\u003e\n',
